top smashing into me so breath sigh of relief, on 2 bubs of health.... woohoo, I'm gonna make it.... run past otters, snash bang wallop biff... we cant stand your kind in our lands... damn the otters are attacking me, the bastids, why???? Run like hell for zone but otters MOVE FAST!!!! ....sigh dead.<br><br>What I finally worked out was that the Sirens had charmed me, I attacked Temparus and the Lupine Dagger proc'd, turning me to doggie form, but the spell icon for doggie form did not appear as I was charmed at the time, when I ran back in doggie form the otters attacked me. sighhh. And to top it all off the cave was just besdie the sirens, so if I had know I could have zoned in there easily!!!<br><br>So we get a rezz and Grunt says zone into SG, stay against the wall, we Succour to the other side, the mobs there wont attack you. Wizard casts Succour, zoning takes a while, arrive to mobs beating the crap out of me.... EEK down to 2 bubs before my screen finishes drawing, run in mad circles trying to work out where to run, by shear luck run after someone and zoned out, had 100hps left.<br><br>Grunt says, okay we run to DN and get to ramp and pull rats, casters bind here at zonein and we have no problems, even if we get wiped out, CR will be a cinch..... (when will I ever learn)....<br><br>Get to ramp and start bashing rats, hey this is good exp, nice loot, easy stuff, woohoo.... get nice and comfy... oops where did that extra rate come from, oh and those 2 bats, and that other rat, and who sprung the trap that casue 6 minny mobs to appear, and what th HELL IS GOING ON HERE!!!! Oopps Kuruk is dead, not good, hmmm coupla others dead, ohh the second group evacced, umm guys, where are yu all going.... Temparus however remained healing me while I fought the last rat, he did a final CH and wished me luck, then camped. <br><br>THE HEROIC LAST MAN STANDING (well LAST WOMEN) is fighting tooth and nail with the MEAN NASTY RAT, we are both on one bub left, this is gonna be very close, I might actually WIN!! WOOHOO what a blast if I win... oops where did that rat go... hmmm rat gated cause he was a chicken, I WIN!!!! Oh no.... you have been summoned.... damn this isnt good... 3 rats jump you and pound the living daylights out of you...hmmm wonder where he gated to...<br><br>To keep it short, they tried to find my corpse but never did, we got Raat (haha funny pun) over to summon my corpse.<br><br>Now was that good enough for you Naps?<br><br><br>Delete Msg | Close Thread | Delete Thread | Copy Thread  <br> <br> Napper <br>   <br>30/04/01 7:51 PM <br><br>IP Address: 139.130.57.140 <br><br>Ban User  RE: Sirens Grotto and Dragon Necropolis - 2 deaths - 28/4/01  <br>   <br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Wow that was fantastic. I felt I was really there ... laughing hehe.<br><br><br>Delete Msg | Close Thread | Delete Thread | Copy Thread  <br> <br> Truc <br>     <br>04/05/01 3:30 AM <br><br> <br><br>IP Address: 65.162.94.168 <br><br>Ban User  RE: Sirens Grotto and Dragon Necropolis - 2 deaths - 28/4/01  <br>   <br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>haha me too naps =) no but really that was a cool story dips. <br> <p><h2>Serendipity</h2><i>Ranger 54 HalfElf</i><br><small>Grindd-Bordd-Boriz-Sihrenity-Vell-Filinsky</small><br><H3>Guild Leader, The Hand</h3></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub61.ezboard.com/fthehand90785frm9.showMessage?topicID=34.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub61.ezboard.com/fthehand90785frm9.showMessage?topicID=32.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub61.ezboard.com/fthehand90785frm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.the-hand.net/forumimages/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> 